RealTimeResultGroupDefinition.SqlString: SELECT Port.Name AS 'Port Name', AllDevice.Name AS 'Device Name', MldRouterResults.McastCompatibilityMode AS 'Multicast Version', MldRouterResults.RouterState AS 'Router State', SUM(MldRouterResults.TxFrameCount) AS 'Tx Frames', SUM(MldRouterResults.RxFrameCount) AS 'Rx Frames', SUM(MldRouterResults.RxUnknownTypeCount) AS 'Rx Unknown Types', SUM(MldRouterResults.RxMldCheckSumErrorCount) AS 'Rx MLD Checksum Errors', SUM(MldRouterResults.RxMldLengthErrorCount) AS 'Rx MLD Length Errors' FROM AllDevice, Port, MldRouterResults, MldRouterConfig, RelationTable WHERE ( RelationTable.Type = 'AffiliationPort' AND RelationTable.SourceHnd = AllDevice.Handle AND RelationTable.TargetHnd = Port.Handle AND MldRouterConfig.ParentHnd = AllDevice.Handle AND MldRouterResults.ParentHnd = MldRouterConfig.Handle AND MldRouterResults.IfHandle = MldRouterConfig.IfHandle AND AllDevice.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND Port.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND MldRouterResults.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND MldRouterConfig.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND RelationTable.DataSetId = @DataSetId ) GROUP BY MldRouterResults.IfHandle
